OL,3,CWhatsApp confirms style shake up for
OL,4,Capp users
OL,6,FWith more than two billion users, it's
OL,7,Fone of the world's biggest messaging
OL,8,Fplatforms. But whether you're a keen
OL,9,Fuser of WhatsApp or just use it from
OL,10,Ftime to time, some seismic changes are
OL,11,Fcoming that will be hard to miss.
OL,13,FA new look, improved features and even
OL,14,Fa slight change to that famous green
OL,15,Fbranding, what else can you expect
OL,16,Ffrom this upcoming update?
OL,18,FA new shade of green
