OL,3,CWhatsApp confirms style shake up for
OL,4,Capp users
OL,6,FSay goodbye to the traditional green
OL,7,FWhatsApp is known for as the company
OL,8,Fis welcoming something a brighter
OL,9,Fgreen, the app's parent company Meta
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FWhatsApp say they considered over 35
OL,13,Fcolour iterations before they chose
OL,14,Fthis new shade.
OL,16,FFor those who prefer dark mode, the
OL,17,Fmessaging app has now introduced a
OL,18,F"darker dark mode" using deeper tones
OL,19,Fand higher contrasts to reduce eye
OL,20,Fstrain when in low light environments.
