OL,3,CWhatsApp confirms style shake up for
OL,4,Capp users
OL,6,FPicture message refresh
OL,8,FBoth icons and illustrations have been
OL,9,Fgiven a refresh. The original default
OL,10,Fbackground has also been redesigned to
OL,11,Fmake it more related to "everyday
OL,12,Fconversations".
OL,14,FAndroid or iPhone users will have a
OL,15,Fsimplified experience when using the
OL,16,Fapp, Meta said.
OL,18,FAndroid users will have a modernised
OL,19,Fnavigation bar to help them find
OL,20,Fcontacts faster.
