OL,3,CWhatsApp confirms style shake up for
OL,4,Capp users
OL,6,FiPhone owners will notice the layout
OL,7,Fhas changed when sending photos and
OL,8,Fvideos. An expandable tray has now
OL,9,Fbeen added, allowing users to see
OL,10,Ffeatures clearly when sending media
OL,11,Fand documents.
OL,13,FEasier to keep track of messages
OL,15,FUsers will now be able to manage their
OL,16,Fconversations better through filters
OL,17,Fwhich Meta says will make it easier to
OL,18,Fmonitor group chats and what you have
OL,19,Fnot yet read.
